########################| HOW TO RUN THE TYPHOID TINA CHANNEL/VIDEO TITLE/COMMENT BLOCKER TAMPERMONKEY SCRIPT |######################
*************************************************************************************************************************************
First, you need to go to Tampermonkey's website tampermonkey.net and add the extension for whatever web browser you use. 
Once you have the extension, copy the Typhoid Tina code precisely as it is on github.
(There is also a copy icon on the top right corner of the code).

Open the Tampermonkey extension. Select "Create a new script..." (it may open a new tab the first time you use it, just close it).
IMPORTANT: delete all of the default code of the new file so the field is blank and you are on line 1 with no spaces. 
Paste the github script into Tampermonkey.
File -> Save to disk -> Name it whatever and save it to whereever you want on your computer as a .js file
You may now manually edit what keywords and channels you would like blocked and hidden after:

const BLOCKED_PHRASES = [
const BLOCKED_TITLE_KEYWORDS = [
const BLOCKED_CHANNELS = [

functions respectively. Just copy the format and syntax of the examples.

Voilà! Now all you have to do is update and save the script any time you make changes!
This may require refreshing the page to take effect. I highly recommend deleting your watch history before enabling the script if your
feed is especially problematic. Enjoy!

BEWARE: I gave an example in BLOCKED_PHRASES = [ in which I included "first",
I advise against using single words for BLOCKED_PHRASES = [ because then it will block all comments with the word "first" in them
regardless of the context or content of the comment itself.

